      • valuesFromTextFile

        public ResultsTable valuesFromTextFile(BufferedInputStream str)
                                throws IOException
        Loads the values of a table stored in a text file as a ResultsTable. Given BufferedInputStream must be marked to hold entire contents in buffer. This method rewinds the buggered stream so it can read it twice.
        Parameters:
        str - The BufferedInputStream containing the data of the text table
        Returns:
        A ResultsTable containing the values (and headers)
        Throws:
        IOException
